2849
02:25:48,130 --> 02:25:49,415
<i>“You two, surrender at once!”</i>

2850
02:25:49,415 --> 02:25:50,700
<i>“And I will spare your master’s life!”</i>

2851
02:25:50,700 --> 02:25:51,985
<i>This, we cannot refuse</i>

2852
02:25:51,985 --> 02:25:53,270
<i>In this, we hold no regrets</i>

2853
02:25:53,270 --> 02:25:54,555
<i>For our queen is our life!</i>

2854
02:25:54,555 --> 02:25:55,840
