were to be executed—

2855
02:25:55,840 --> 02:25:57,125
I’ll give you a little souvenir
before your trip to Hell!

2856
02:25:57,125 --> 02:25:58,410
Your master isn’t being held in the tower.

2857
02:25:58,410 --> 02:25:59,695
I cut off her head myself just yesterday!

2858
02:25:59,695 --> 02:26:00,980
Look at her lying over
there like a piece of rubbish!

2859
02:26:00,980 --> 02:26:02,265
